STATE
v.
Ailkeem Anthony NORMAN 153PA17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 1, 2017 Mr. Ben G. Irons, II, Attorney at Law, For Norman, Ailkeem Anthony. Mr. Douglas W. Corkhill, Assistant Attorney General, For State of North Carolina. Mr. Seth H. Edwards, District Attorney, For State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th of May 2017 by State of NC for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Dissolved by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st of November 2017."
